'''聯結主義'''（{{lang-en|Connectionism}}）是[[认知科学|认知科学]]领域的一种方法，期望能夠以[[人工神经网络|人工神经網路]]（ANN）来解释[[心灵|心靈]]现象。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://plato.stanford.edu/archives/fall2018/entries/connectionism/|title=The Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy|first=James|last=Garson|editor-first=Edward N.|editor-last=Zalta|date=27 November 2018|publisher=Metaphysics Research Lab, Stanford University|access-date=2019-09-24|archive-date=2020-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725124833/https://plato.stanford.edu/archives/fall2018/entries/connectionism/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
